  "text": "Whilst some therapeutics described in this review are still under active investigation as exemplified by frequent and continuing publication of new findings, some approaches show large gaps or halts in the published literature. This suggests that perhaps findings could not be replicated by other groups or in other HD models studied with negative results not reaching traditional published literature outlets due to publication bias [CITATION_1] . Therefore, the validity of certain therapeutics suggested in limited numbers of studies should be analysed and evaluated cautiously.",
